With my favorite travel buddy 🥰

We actually didn’t know we would be seeing the Taj Mahal. It was a surprise and one of the most incredible things I’ve seen! @vadster on top of having her own wedding (which was three to four days full of festivities) planned an amazing trip afterwards for us. Instead of a honeymoon, she chose a “friend” moon. I’m not sure how many people would choose to do that but it shows you how special she is, along with Parth. Thank you for the opportunity and treating us like family ❤️ It’s crazy how we almost didn’t go, due to the Coronavirus. Our first flights got cancelled and we weren’t sure about traveling. we made it back “just in time.” I miss traveling and seeing friends and family. Hoping the world can heal soon! Stay safe everyone. 
Virtual hugs and dances 🤗💃🏽 Join @rumbao_ldc for online classes!
